title: Threedom returns for Season 3!
description: Threedom is back, free to listen to everywhere October 22nd! You'll also be able to hear the first five episodes early on Stitcher Premium; for a free month, just go to stitcherpremium.com and use the promo code THREEDOM.
author: fanmail@earwolf.com (Earwolf & Scott Aukerman, Paul F Tompkins, Lauren Lapkus)
